# Sales Performance Analysis & Business KPIs

## Business Context
This notebook performs exploratory data analysis (EDA) and calculates key
business KPIs to evaluate sales performance, customer behavior, and regional trends.

The insights generated will support management decision-making and dashboard development.
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import seaborn as sns
# Load cleaned data
df = pd.read_csv("../data/cleaned_sales_data.csv")

# Preview data
df.head()
df.shape
df.info()
total_revenue = df["Revenue"].sum()
total_profit = df["Estimated_Profit"].sum()

total_revenue, total_profit
aov = df["Revenue"].mean()
aov
customer_summary = df.groupby("Customer_Type")["Customer_ID"].nunique()
customer_summary
retention_rate = (
    customer_summary["Repeat"] /
    customer_summary.sum()
) * 100

retention_rate
monthly_revenue = df.groupby("Month")["Revenue"].sum().reset_index()

monthly_revenue
plt.figure()
plt.bar(monthly_revenue["Month"], monthly_revenue["Revenue"])
plt.title("Monthly Revenue Trend")
plt.xlabel("Month")
plt.ylabel("Revenue")
plt.xticks(rotation=45)
plt.show()
region_revenue = df.groupby("Region")["Revenue"].sum().sort_values(ascending=False)

region_revenue
plt.figure()
region_revenue.plot(kind="bar")
plt.title("Revenue by Region")
plt.xlabel("Region")
plt.ylabel("Revenue")
plt.show()
category_revenue = df.groupby("Product_Category")["Revenue"].sum()

category_revenue
plt.figure()
category_revenue.plot(kind="bar")
plt.title("Revenue by Product Category")
plt.xlabel("Category")
plt.ylabel("Revenue")
plt.show()

top_products = (
    df.groupby("Product_Name")["Revenue"]
    .sum()
    .sort_values(ascending=False)
    .head(5)
)

top_products
df["Revenue_Level"].value_counts()
plt.figure()
df["Revenue_Level"].value_counts().plot(kind="pie", autopct="%1.1f%%")
plt.title("Revenue Distribution by Level")
plt.ylabel("")
plt.show()
customer_revenue = df.groupby("Customer_Type")["Revenue"].sum()
customer_revenue
plt.figure()
customer_revenue.plot(kind="bar")
plt.title("Revenue by Customer Type")
plt.xlabel("Customer Type")
plt.ylabel("Revenue")
plt.show()
payment_revenue = df.groupby("Payment_Mode")["Revenue"].sum()
payment_revenue
region_profit = df.groupby("Region")["Estimated_Profit"].sum()

region_profit
## Key Insights
- Electronics contribute the highest revenue among all categories
- Repeat customers generate higher revenue compared to new customers
- West and South regions outperform other regions
- High revenue transactions form a smaller percentage but contribute
  significantly to overall revenue

## Business Recommendations
- Introduce loyalty programs to increase repeat customer base
- Focus marketing efforts on high-performing regions
- Promote high-margin electronics products

## Conclusion
This analysis provided a clear understanding of sales performance,
customer behavior, and regional trends.

The insights derived can be used to:
- Build executive dashboards
- Support strategic business decisions
- Improve customer retention and revenue growth

